Package: xcmsVisGUI
Title: Interactive Raw LC-MS Viewer (Shiny)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Jan", "Stanstrup", email = "stanstrup@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A local Shiny desktop application for interactively visualising raw
    LC-MS data on the RforMassSpectrometry stack (Spectra, MsExperiment, xcms),
    delegating all plotting to the xcmsVis package. Features asynchronous file
    reading, file inclusion control, rich filtering, multiple EICs per file,
    click-to-spectrum, 2D/3D maps, and publication-quality export.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
